find this great housekeeper?

246
00:15:18,633 --> 00:15:19,633
Her cooking's phenomenal.

247
00:15:20,113 --> 00:15:22,034
She's more like family than staff.

248
00:15:22,633 --> 00:15:23,554
I got lucky

249
00:15:23,554 --> 00:15:25,034
finding Ms. Lu on my first try.

250
00:15:25,074 --> 00:15:26,314
She's been working for me.

251
00:15:31,353 --> 00:15:32,473
If you're that close,

252
00:15:32,473 --> 00:15:33,993
why does she call you 'Miss Nie'?

253
00:15:34,074 --> 00:15:35,113
It sounds so formal.

254
00:15:37,633 --> 00:15:39,074
I've actually told her many times

255
00:15:39,713 --> 00:15:40,873
to just call me Luo.

256
00:15:41,274 --> 00:15:43,034
But Ms. Lu insists boundaries are needed

257
00:15:43,034 --> 00:15:44,554
for employer-employee relationships.

258
00:15:44,954 --> 00:15:46,233
Hence the Miss Nie title.

259
00:15:46,633 --> 00:15:47,753
I respect her choice.

260
00:16:01,113 --> 00:16:01,833
What did you say?

261
00:16:06,954 --> 00:16:07,554
Can...

262
00:16:10,034 --> 00:16:11,034
Can I call you Luo?

263
00:16:19,074 --> 00:16:19,674
Okay.

264
00:16:38,513 --> 00:16:41,034
These are all your diaries?

265
00:16:43,194 --> 00:16:45,034
You have my permission
to pick one to read.

266
00:16:45,674 --> 00:16:46,233
