316
00:20:30,114 --> 00:20:31,394
You may go there anytime.

317
00:20:43,273 --> 00:20:44,354
Mr. Yan, please.

318
00:20:44,594 --> 00:20:45,233
Thank you.

319
00:20:45,450 --> 00:20:49,776
♪Cold, warm, and tepid light
is sculpting♪

320
00:20:50,954 --> 00:20:54,921
♪The contour of your side face
by the pillow♪

321
00:20:56,953 --> 00:21:01,710
♪One, two split stars are writing♪

322
00:21:02,396 --> 00:21:06,595
♪The scenes only you're in♪

323
00:21:07,886 --> 00:21:13,780
♪Awake, torn, or unbound,
I'm not the only one♪

324
00:21:13,966 --> 00:21:18,336
♪Escaping the vortex
of underwater memories♪

325
00:21:19,632 --> 00:21:25,257
♪Missing in my heart, seeing you appear♪

326
00:21:25,500 --> 00:21:29,960
♪It's the sunny day after the rain♪

327
00:21:31,166 --> 00:21:36,808
♪So I smile, I forget,
and I'm not panicking♪

328
00:21:37,099 --> 00:21:41,332
♪Tireless, and fearless of absurdity♪

329
00:21:42,665 --> 00:21:45,713
♪Look at the strong wind sweeping by♪

330
00:21:45,846 --> 00:21:48,409
♪Look at the heavy rain pouring down♪

331
00:21:48,993 --> 00:21:51,154
(If you can't be someone's support,)

332
00:21:51,154 --> 00:21:53,594
(at least don't drag her
into your whirlpool.)

333
00:21:54,538 --> 00:21:58,512
♪The night sky sparks for you and me♪

334
00:23:02,993 --> 00:23:03,993
His name is

335
00:23:04,914 --> 00:23:05,954
Qin Chi, right?

336
00:23:07,313 --> 00:23:08,793
That's what the file says.

337
00:23:11,313 --> 00:23:12,033
My fault.

338
00:23:12,674 --> 00:23:13,954
It was a poorly chosen name.

339
00:23:14,993 --> 00:23:16,513
He truly arrived too late.

340
00:23:18,793 --> 00:23:19,834
Very few people

341
00:23:20,914 --> 00:23:21,954
can access this place.

342
00:23:23,634 --> 00:23:25,553
We couldn't reach Li Yueying?

343
00:23:27,273 --> 00:23:28,354
The mine sent word.

344
00:23:29,033 --> 00:23:30,354
Li Yueying went there.

345
00:23:37,033 --> 00:23:38,793
I do owe her.

346
00:23:41,394 --> 00:23:42,594
Let's go to the mine.

347
00:23:43,233 --> 00:23:44,594
You two clean this up.

348
00:23:46,033 --> 00:23:47,154
Should I accompany you?

349
00:23:47,280 --> 00:23:48,600
Xiong Hei and Feng Mi can stay...

350
00:24:41,313 --> 00:24:41,954
Why?

351
00:24:46,674 --> 00:24:47,674
Does it matter?

352
00:25:08,354 --> 00:25:09,553
I was the first

353
00:25:10,194 --> 00:25:11,634
to emerge from below.

354
00:25:12,553 --> 00:25:13,753
I survived

355
00:25:14,394 --> 00:25:15,874
only by heaven's mercy.

356
00:25:17,114 --> 00:25:19,434
When I first saw the world

357
00:25:19,674 --> 00:25:21,354
in human form under sunlight,

358
00:25:22,553 --> 00:25:23,954
I felt no relief,

359
00:25:24,394 --> 00:25:25,394
only fear.

360
00:25:26,713 --> 00:25:28,594
Even after consuming that miner,

361
00:25:28,834 --> 00:25:30,154
my first blood bag,

362
00:25:30,594 --> 00:25:32,793
and my body stabilized,

363
00:25:33,753 --> 00:25:36,874
and I even learned to blend
into human society,

364
00:25:37,594 --> 00:25:39,553
the fear remained.

365
00:25:42,513 --> 00:25:44,473
Do you know when

366
00:25:45,033 --> 00:25:46,273
my fear finally faded?

367
00:25:49,914 --> 00:25:51,394
It was when I saw you

368
00:25:51,874 --> 00:25:53,553
successfully transformed too.

369
00:25:54,914 --> 00:25:56,793
My heart found peace at last.

370
00:25:58,194 --> 00:25:59,434
In this world,

371
00:26:00,473 --> 00:26:02,834
I was no longer a lonely aberration.

372
00:26:07,634 --> 00:26:09,434
You call this success?

373
00:26:12,954 --> 00:26:14,713
We had no experience back then.

374
00:26:16,394 --> 00:26:19,194
In haste, I made you eat that blood bag.

375
00:26:20,713 --> 00:26:23,033
You became alarmingly weak,

376
00:26:23,194 --> 00:26:24,914
even losing consciousness.

377
00:26:25,914 --> 00:26:27,993
Only then did we realize
the blood bag was tainted

378
00:26:29,634 --> 00:26:31,033
and couldn't produce offspring.

379
00:26:33,434 --> 00:26:35,713
All companions from your batch

380
00:26:36,473 --> 00:26:37,993
failed to survive.

381
00:26:40,114 --> 00:26:42,753
During those bleak, hopeless days,

382
00:26:43,354 --> 00:26:44,194
only you

383
00:26:44,753 --> 00:26:46,394
had seen the outside world.

384
00:26:51,553 --> 00:26:52,394
Filthy.

385
00:26:53,114 --> 00:26:53,793
Dark.

386
00:26:54,634 --> 00:26:55,394
Foul-smelling.

387
00:26:56,993 --> 00:26:59,594
Those are human prejudices about sewers.

388
00:27:01,313 --> 00:27:03,033
But for rats,

389
00:27:05,194 --> 00:27:06,354
it's paradise.

390
00:27:08,273 --> 00:27:09,634
To you,

391
00:27:10,033 --> 00:27:12,154
wearing this human shell

392
00:27:13,033 --> 00:27:15,753
and feeling sunlight and greenery

393
00:27:16,553 --> 00:27:18,194
is a divine blessing.

394
00:27:19,273 --> 00:27:22,874
But I only feel dread, loss,

395
00:27:23,674 --> 00:27:24,954
and disorientation.

396
00:27:26,513 --> 00:27:28,553
How could you make me

397
00:27:28,553 --> 00:27:30,594
live in this half-dead body

398
00:27:31,713 --> 00:27:33,434
and pretend obedience

399
00:27:33,914 --> 00:27:35,713
before you,

400
00:27:37,073 --> 00:27:38,874
feigning gratitude?

401
00:27:39,194 --> 00:27:41,634
So you'd kill your own
whose roots aren't removed?

402
00:27:43,194 --> 00:27:45,753
The method for safe root removal

403
00:27:46,354 --> 00:27:49,154
was discovered
through our joint efforts.

404
00:27:50,753 --> 00:27:53,233
They became robust,

405
00:27:53,713 --> 00:27:54,954
ageless, and strong,

406
00:27:56,073 --> 00:27:58,154
taking it for granted.

407
00:28:00,434 --> 00:28:03,114
They look at me with pity,

408
00:28:04,114 --> 00:28:06,033
as if I'm defective

409
00:28:07,073 --> 00:28:08,513
and I'm a monster.

410
00:28:11,273 --> 00:28:12,033
Fine.

411
00:28:12,914 --> 00:28:13,914
It doesn't matter.

412
00:28:14,354 --> 00:28:15,793
None of that matters.

413
00:28:18,354 --> 00:28:19,793
But when I saw you

414
00:28:19,793 --> 00:28:22,233
execute Gou Ya without blinking

415
00:28:23,594 --> 00:28:26,834
and justify it as 'following rules,'

416
00:28:29,313 --> 00:28:31,354
I finally understood

417
00:28:33,313 --> 00:28:35,194
that my days are numbered.

418
00:28:37,073 --> 00:28:38,154
I just hoped

419
00:28:38,753 --> 00:28:40,194
my future companions

420
00:28:41,954 --> 00:28:44,233
would never come to this human world.

421
00:28:47,273 --> 00:28:47,954
No.

422
00:28:49,273 --> 00:28:51,114
This isn't the human world.

423
00:28:52,954 --> 00:28:54,834
It's purgatory.

424
00:29:05,713 --> 00:29:06,874
The sun is about to rise.

425
00:29:09,033 --> 00:29:10,473
You should head back now.

426
00:30:37,753 --> 00:30:38,473
Ms. Lu,

427
00:30:39,753 --> 00:30:40,513
where's Yan Tuo?

428
00:30:42,033 --> 00:30:42,993
You're awake.

429
00:30:43,553 --> 00:30:44,914
He left early this morning.

430
00:30:56,330 --> 00:31:00,938
(Work is piling up. I need to handle it.
Rest well, and contact me anytime.)

431
00:31:07,154 --> 00:31:08,394
Alright, Miss Nie.

432
00:31:08,834 --> 00:31:09,954
Time for some exercise.

433
00:31:10,674 --> 00:31:11,513
What exercise?

434
00:31:12,473 --> 00:31:13,194
To rehabilitate.

435
00:31:13,594 --> 00:31:15,073
Mr. Yan ordered the equipment.

436
00:31:15,594 --> 00:31:16,634
I've been busy with it

437
00:31:16,793 --> 00:31:17,713
all this morning.

438
00:31:54,513 --> 00:31:55,154
Shift change.

439
00:31:55,713 --> 00:31:58,313
I just fell asleep.

440
00:31:58,753 --> 00:32:00,434
Stop whining. Get up.

441
00:32:01,253 --> 00:32:01,753
Bro.

442
00:32:01,753 --> 00:32:02,273
Up!

443
00:32:02,273 --> 00:32:03,154
Bro.

444
00:32:03,154 --> 00:32:03,753
It hurts.

445
00:32:04,154 --> 00:32:04,713
It hurts.

446
00:32:04,993 --> 00:32:06,154
I've been searching forever.

447
00:32:06,354 --> 00:32:07,713
Fine, I'll go.

448
00:32:09,793 --> 00:32:10,753
Sleep carefully.

449
00:32:10,753 --> 00:32:11,553
It's full of bugs.

450
00:32:21,753 --> 00:32:23,273
Before Mr. Yan left,

451
00:32:23,753 --> 00:32:25,793
he kept telling me

452
00:32:25,874 --> 00:32:27,434
to take good care of you.

453
00:32:29,313 --> 00:32:30,313
When he left,

454
00:32:31,473 --> 00:32:33,273
he wanted to pick an osmanthus branch.

455
00:32:34,033 --> 00:32:34,713
I stopped him.

456
00:32:35,753 --> 00:32:36,553
Why?

457
00:32:40,354 --> 00:32:41,513
I mean,

458
00:32:41,954 --> 00:32:43,114
he saved my life.

459
00:32:43,594 --> 00:32:44,753
Picking one flower branch

460
00:32:45,073 --> 00:32:46,233
shouldn't be a big deal.

461
00:32:46,914 --> 00:32:47,914
I told him

462
00:32:48,354 --> 00:32:49,473
plucked flowers

463
00:32:49,553 --> 00:32:50,874
lose their fragrance quickly.

464
00:32:51,233 --> 00:32:52,394
I suggested he should

465
00:32:52,513 --> 00:32:53,993
visit more often to enjoy the blooms.

466
00:33:03,313 --> 00:33:04,033
Mr. Changxi.

467
00:33:04,753 --> 00:33:06,793
Miss Nie, how's your recovery going?

468
00:33:07,954 --> 00:33:09,954
Much better now. Thank you.

469
00:33:10,674 --> 00:33:11,553
Well,

470
00:33:11,993 --> 00:33:13,073
my attic

471
00:33:13,073 --> 00:33:14,793
might have aging floorboards.

472
00:33:14,954 --> 00:33:17,233
I keep hearing creaking noises lately.

473
00:33:17,834 --> 00:33:19,194
With the recent rains,

474
00:33:19,473 --> 00:33:20,954
I fear your items might get damp.

475
00:33:21,434 --> 00:33:23,114
Should I move them elsewhere for you?

476
00:33:23,114 --> 00:33:23,834
Mr. Changxi,

477
00:33:24,914 --> 00:33:26,553
I actually need

478
00:33:26,594 --> 00:33:27,753
to use those soon.

479
00:33:28,073 --> 00:33:29,273
No need to trouble you.

480
00:33:29,273 --> 00:33:30,713
I'll come get them myself later.

481
00:33:31,553 --> 00:33:33,713
Alright. Come anytime. I'll be here.

482
00:33:34,313 --> 00:33:35,834
Great. Thanks, Mr. Changxi.

483
00:34:04,434 --> 00:34:07,313
Yuwang Meat often mixes
within Turquoise Land.

484
00:34:08,113 --> 00:34:09,874
The purest one resembles a jellyfish

485
00:34:10,153 --> 00:34:10,993
with a jade sheen.

486
00:34:11,314 --> 00:34:13,914
It feels like rich butter
and glows by night.

487
00:34:14,513 --> 00:34:17,354
Ancient South Mountain hunter Tu
one found it.

488
00:34:17,473 --> 00:34:19,754
His hounds ate it
and then preyed on rabbits.

489
00:34:19,754 --> 00:34:21,394
They died suddenly that day.

490
00:34:22,113 --> 00:34:23,714
Their corpses buried in Turquoise Land

491
00:34:23,834 --> 00:34:25,633
rotted and spawned strange beasts.

492
00:34:25,993 --> 00:34:28,593
They had long ears, sharp teeth,
red eyes, and mad howls,

493
00:34:28,754 --> 00:34:31,354
resembling hounds and rabbits,
yet they were no hound or rabbit.

494
00:34:35,113 --> 00:34:36,874
Resembling hounds and rabbits,

495
00:34:38,274 --> 00:34:39,633
yet neither hound nor rabbit.

496
00:34:40,434 --> 00:34:41,633
So Yuwang Meat

497
00:34:42,834 --> 00:34:45,234
could merge two species.

498
00:34:49,113 --> 00:34:49,633
Well...

499
00:34:54,754 --> 00:34:56,153
South Mountain County Chronicles.

500
00:34:57,033 --> 00:34:59,274
Yuwang Meat regenerates endlessly

501
00:34:59,513 --> 00:35:01,714
and regrows to its original form.

502
00:35:01,954 --> 00:35:04,073
Eating it strengthens vitality,

503
00:35:04,673 --> 00:35:06,754
granting the longevity
of the turtle and the crane.

504
00:35:06,954 --> 00:35:09,673
Its eaters must retreat
from the mortal world

505
00:35:09,794 --> 00:35:12,553
and cultivate immortality in mountains.

506
00:35:13,314 --> 00:35:15,874
The emperor sought immortality methods

507
00:35:16,193 --> 00:35:18,314
and sent officials
to sail east for elixirs.

508
00:35:18,874 --> 00:35:21,354
Qin troops entered South Mountain

509
00:35:21,513 --> 00:35:22,754
for this very reason.

510
00:35:23,993 --> 00:35:25,434
Immortality?

511
00:35:40,938 --> 00:35:46,576
(Ancient Texts)

512
00:35:55,354 --> 00:35:56,834
There was another named Han Guan.

513
00:35:56,834 --> 00:35:58,033
I've already dealt with him.

514
00:35:58,593 --> 00:35:59,633
This one's Chen Fu.

515
00:35:59,914 --> 00:36:01,234
No space to hide at my place.

516
00:36:06,714 --> 00:36:08,274
Leave him here. It's safe.

517
00:36:14,394 --> 00:36:15,314
Recently,

518
00:36:15,593 --> 00:36:17,954
I sorted out Earth Fiends'
human-transformation logic

519
00:36:18,073 --> 00:36:19,193
and got the basic pattern.

520
00:36:20,593 --> 00:36:21,314
Go ahead.

521
00:36:23,354 --> 00:36:24,673
When Earth Fiends become human,

522
00:36:25,153 --> 00:36:26,394
they need human nutrients

523
00:36:26,394 --> 00:36:27,794
to maintain their forms.

524
00:36:29,193 --> 00:36:29,954
Such humans

525
00:36:31,354 --> 00:36:32,234
are called blood bags.

526
00:36:34,434 --> 00:36:37,314
So they must constantly capture humans.

527
00:36:37,794 --> 00:36:38,714
It's more complicated.

528
00:36:39,513 --> 00:36:41,513
Blood bags require strict selection.

529
00:36:42,314 --> 00:36:44,673
Each generation
must be a direct bloodline.

530
00:36:46,234 --> 00:36:47,394
Otherwise,

531
00:36:48,073 --> 00:36:49,434
Earth Fiends commit omnivory,

532
00:36:50,153 --> 00:36:51,954
letting Hound Clan smell them

533
00:36:52,234 --> 00:36:53,113
and expose themselves.

534
00:36:54,113 --> 00:36:56,673
When Big Head smelled a fiendish scent
in Yan Tuo's car

535
00:36:57,354 --> 00:36:58,794
because Gou Ya in the trunk

536
00:36:58,794 --> 00:37:00,193
omnivorized in the welfare home.

537
00:37:00,834 --> 00:37:02,434
If the requirements are this strict,

538
00:37:04,874 --> 00:37:06,153
how can they ensure

539
00:37:06,434 --> 00:37:08,234
the continuous supply of the blood bags?

540
00:37:09,434 --> 00:37:10,593
To control the blood bags,

541
00:37:11,234 --> 00:37:12,553
the Earth Fiends live with them

542
00:37:12,553 --> 00:37:13,874
as family members.

543
00:37:15,473 --> 00:37:17,434
Just like Chen Fu's girlfriend, Xu Anni,

544
00:37:18,473 --> 00:37:19,633
who never knew

545
00:37:19,633 --> 00:37:20,993
that she was in danger.

546
00:37:21,954 --> 00:37:23,234
If the blood bags

547
00:37:23,234 --> 00:37:24,993
are merely
their life-extending medicine,

548
00:37:25,593 --> 00:37:26,754
what exactly is the key

549
00:37:26,914 --> 00:37:29,153
that first transformed the Earth Fiends

550
00:37:30,553 --> 00:37:31,553
from beasts to humans?

551
00:37:39,274 --> 00:37:40,513
I'll wake him and question him.

552
00:37:41,874 --> 00:37:42,914
I've already done that.

553
00:37:43,234 --> 00:37:44,874
He didn't reveal any useful information.

554
00:37:46,033 --> 00:37:47,354
He even bit his own tongue.

555
00:37:48,394 --> 00:37:49,314
The Earth Fiends now

556
00:37:49,993 --> 00:37:51,553
not only possess human intelligence,

557
00:37:51,553 --> 00:37:52,683
consciousness, and emotions,

558
00:37:52,944 --> 00:37:54,354
but also have developed integrity.

559
00:37:56,914 --> 00:37:57,794
They have long

560
00:37:57,993 --> 00:37:59,794
been different from the beasts

561
00:37:59,794 --> 00:38:00,524
our ancestors saw.

562
00:38:02,874 --> 00:38:03,633
How do you know

563
00:38:04,673 --> 00:38:06,033
all these things?

564
00:38:06,754 --> 00:38:08,153
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

565
00:38:11,754 --> 00:38:13,274
Something came up and delayed me.

566
00:38:14,434 --> 00:38:15,914
Thankfully, Yan Tuo helped out.

567
00:38:16,193 --> 00:38:17,234
It was a close call.

568
00:38:22,553 --> 00:38:23,193
Luo,

569
00:38:25,234 --> 00:38:26,193
you're Mad Blade.

570
00:38:27,473 --> 00:38:29,714
Mingling with someone
from the fiends' den,

571
00:38:30,794 --> 00:38:32,394
don't you fear he has ulterior motives?

572
00:38:41,193 --> 00:38:42,073
I judge people

573
00:38:42,794 --> 00:38:44,113
with my own discernment.

574
00:38:44,794 --> 00:38:46,033
You don't need to worry.

